Introducing the Reverso Discovery Workshop.
#AtelierAntoine
_
Atelier d’Antoine
The Reverso Discovery Workshop
_
At the heart of the Vallée de Joux, enter the Manufacture Jaeger-LeCoultre for an unforgettable experience. 90 years after the birth of Reverso, Atelier d’Antoine presents a unique opportunity to discover the inside story of the watchmaking icon, from its historic origins to its unique craftsmanship. Guided by our experts, learn how to assemble a Reverso case by yourself, with no less than 50 components.
_
